data.title: Chump Definition & Meaning
data.meta_description: Chump definition: A gullible person; a dupe.
data.text:
The cost is mere chump change to a wealthy heiress like Paris Hilton.

Meanwhile, a reader wrote and she said what could she be doing in her garden during January, silly chump.

May be more expensive than loin chumps but chump chops are larger and meatier.

Never smarten up a chump, as Barnum said.
